ThyssenKrupp May Build Factory in Slovakia, Hospodarske Says

-- B y   R a d o s l a v   T o m e k
-- 
2011-08-03T07:04:28Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-03/thyssenkrupp-may-build-factory-in-slovakia-hospodarske-says.html
ThyssenKrupp AG (TKA)  is considering to
build a factory in Slovakia,  Hospodarske Noviny  reported, citing
an unidentified senior economy ministry official.  The German steelmaker may employ as many as 1,200 people in
the new plant supplying car makers in the region, the newspaper
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Radoslav Tomek in Bratislava at 
 rtomek@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James Gomez at   jagomez@bloomberg.net . 